          "story_image": "shopify://shop_images/bare_earth.png",
          "story_body": "<p>As part of the Sarom family, we spent years helping people create beautiful homes through thoughtfully crafted fabrics and home furnishings. Along the way, we realized that one of the most personal spaces in every home deserved the same attention, the bedroom.</p><p>That's how Beds & More began.</p><p>Today, we bring together quality materials, timeless designs, and everyday comfort to create bedding that's made to be lived in, loved, and enjoyed for years to come.</p><p>Thoughtfully crafted for the moments you come home to.</p>",
